data.eml:eml: Osteological description of Pseudopaludicola canga with implications for the taxonomic position of this taxon

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cardozo, Darío, Suárez, Pablo (2012): Osteological description of Pseudopaludicola canga with implications for the taxonomic position of this taxon. Zootaxa 3515: 75-82, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.282591
